ps0SetUnPinDesc: Close the panel after the task is complete.
ps0AddAlternateDesc: Add alternates for the object. An alternate is a replacement for an object in all product configurations. To add replacements in a specific assembly, use substitutes.
ps0RemoveAlternateDesc: Remove the selected alternates from the object. An alternate is a replacement for an object in all product configurations.
unitEffectivityTooltip:
Validate ranges:
*Unit value should be positive value
Start Unit (Ex: 5)
*Start unit value cannot less than End Unit
Start Unit-End Unit (Ex: 5-7)
Start Unit-SO (Ex: 5-SO)
Start Unit-UP (Ex:-5-UP)
Start Unit 1-End Unit 1(Ex: 5-7)
ps0CreateBaselineDesc: Create a baseline to capture the interim state of the structure as new revisions with baseline status, which can be used for informal collaboration without changing the original content.
